      <title>奥地利在经济衰退的阴影中安装新的机柜，最右边</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/austria-installs-new-cabinet-in-shadow-of-recession-far-right</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大选后五个月，奥地利任命了一个保守党领导的政府，该政府委托经济摆脱了衰退，同时减少了预算赤字并扭转了右翼民粹主义的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/austria-installs-new-cabinet-in-shadow-of-recession-far-right</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 10:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰计划简化国防规则以支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ireland-plans-to-ease-defense-rules-to-support-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰政府将提出更改其在国外派遣部队的规则，因为中立国家加大了对乌克兰的实际支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ireland-plans-to-ease-defense-rules-to-support-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 10:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税威胁下，墨西哥的明星经济梦想崩溃了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/mexico-economic-dreams-crumble-under-trump-s-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[仅仅几年前，制造商一直在为墨西哥东北部工业城市的蒙特雷（Monterrey）搬迁空间，因为他们试图更靠近美国及其庞大的消费市场。如今，房地产经纪人提供了灵活的租赁计划，以将企业保留在该地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/mexico-economic-dreams-crumble-under-trump-s-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国探索国防和基础设施支出的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/germany-explores-options-for-defense-and-infrastructure-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧洲的大量支出以提高大陆的安全性，这两个政党可能组成由保守派弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz）领导的德国下一个政府正在探索大规模投资于国防和基础设施的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/germany-explores-options-for-defense-and-infrastructure-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰的债券随着特朗普的争执席卷东欧交易而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年重组以来，乌克兰的美元债券是美国和欧洲对和平进程之间的分裂以来最多的，这使投资者期望有序地朝着停火前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非最大的政党任命新的经济政策负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/south-africa-s-biggest-party-appoints-new-economic-policy-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲国民大会是南非最大的政党，在对其内部结构进行大修中任命Zuko Godlimpi为经济转型委员会的负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/south-africa-s-biggest-party-appoints-new-economic-policy-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:03:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查发现，加拿大人在消费者抗议中避开亚马逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canadians-shun-amazon-in-consumer-protest-against-us-poll-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数加拿大消费者表示，自美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）升级他对加拿大的威胁以来，他们已经退缩了购买美国制造的产品，并且在Amazon.com Inc.上购物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canadians-shun-amazon-in-consumer-protest-against-us-poll-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy说他会再次与特朗普见面，但不惜一切代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/zelenskiy-says-he-s-ready-to-meet-trump-again-if-invited-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）说，如果美国总统邀请他邀请他，他愿意再次与唐纳德·特朗普会面，但表明他遇到另一场白宫的遇到必须是“认真的”，他要这次旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/zelenskiy-says-he-s-ready-to-meet-trump-again-if-invited-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 23:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙告诉法国菲加罗，英国制作乌克兰休战计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/france-uk-working-on-one-month-truce-in-ukraine-macron-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）和英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）正在制定一项计划在乌克兰进行一个月的休战计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/france-uk-working-on-one-month-truce-in-ukraine-macron-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 22:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对哈马斯的立场强化了，特朗普勇敢地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/israel-signals-hardened-stance-toward-hamas-emboldened-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列决定在一年多以来首次切断对加沙的人道主义援助，这表明该组织拒绝了美国领导的停火提议，以提出对哈马斯的零容忍态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/israel-signals-hardened-stance-toward-hamas-emboldened-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 16:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
